{"tid":824404,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日靚午餐 地中海燴牛肩肉配焗薯仔、蠶豆、迷你洋蔥","createTime":"2018-09-17T05:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T04:43:39.000Z","uid":33359,"like":57,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"46af35b394f03f604f73de5f04c9b3075d63259b","tid":824404,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/131830_09ca7aef44c9fe2f6d21a9c725290b8b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F131830_09ca7aef44c9fe2f6d21a9c725290b8b.png&h=beb23957&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d4a51dfe6328106ea2cf9b0e066a68e03b4508b","tid":824404,"uid":198810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4615a5aade4ae20f6e8f50be0cb1a12523ee5884","tid":824404,"uid":30037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"搵日幫手試下加洲風情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d831bc0a72b2b65f604b58a3cabdeead1b8f41","tid":824404,"uid":139010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"仲迫緊地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dafc0763ca8a7754b974f539cb65e77f5e420b3","tid":824404,"uid":113064,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T05:22:35.000Z","msg":"一剔過<br />\nA、B、C、D餐係固定午餐<br />\n而E、F、G、H餐係每星期都轉一次<br />\n連埋蒜包餐湯凍飲 原價$45 / 48 / 50蚊<br />\n1230前埋單 / 1415後入坐減5蚊<br />\n盛惠$40 / 43 / 45蚊<br />\n推介菜式係皇牌燒雞 + 避風塘脆薯皇<br />\n星期六會送埋甜品 暫時係焦糖燉蛋<br />\n有緣仲會見到連登飲食台<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>堅硬台柱</strong></span><br />\n百里香<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>御用頂